{"tid":2496715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《日本人如何區分中國人》髮型穿著講聲？網友各自提出獨創分辨法……","createTime":"2021-04-20T04:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:32:20.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"982bbf14df2c15c06dbcc9e08de881e2dcd950c9","tid":2496715,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1662798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1662798&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=dc7c6fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1662798</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU8JfVY9aTcRiq7NhwXLi6pdsuZKrZvhhs1ZUxA81pHEz?filename=igDCWYW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigDCWYW.png&h=df3d730b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：鯛魚<br />\n<br />\n你覺得東亞各國的人都長得一模一樣嗎？還是你能夠精準辨每個國家的獨特風格呢？有一篇關於「日本人如何認出中國人」的文章最近被翻譯成日文以後，在日本討論區與推特引發熱烈迴響，文中提及髮型、穿著、禮儀、衛生習慣、講話的音量等等多方面分析，不過日本網友也並非完全同意這篇文章，因此又各自提出獨到的分辨方法，想必在接下來的中國國慶連假之際，這些分辨方法應該能夠獲得更進一步的驗證吧！大家又覺得這些特徵準不準呢？<br />\n<br />\n「看起來明明都一樣，為什麼日本人能夠一眼認出中國人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKU.jpg&h=05f21abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"http://news.searchina.net/id/1682752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.searchina.net%2Fid%2F1682752&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=30bb9bb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.searchina.net/id/1682752</a><br />\n<br />\n這一篇統整中國網站關於「日本人如何區分中國人」話題的文章最近在日本討論區與推特引發迴響，文中提到「不顧旁人」、「吵吵鬧鬧」、「不在意穿衣打扮」、「亂丟垃圾」等等特徵，不過日本網友們也紛紛提出自己的見解&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「當然是大聲說中文才會被認為是中國人啊，大聲說日文就會被當成日本人了吧」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKY.jpg&h=525d0ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joker0818/status/1175006930617528320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoker0818%2Fstatus%2F1175006930617528320&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=2c5665ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoker0818%2Fstatus%2F1175006930617528320&h=b7b56b51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joker0818/status/1175006930617528320</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「從近處立刻能夠感受到他們有夠吵，從遠處則是看服裝就能察覺」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKc.jpg&h=46504041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jirozzz/status/1175305089541529600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjirozzz%2Fstatus%2F1175305089541529600&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=cad34d51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjirozzz%2Fstatus%2F1175305089541529600&h=57abc234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jirozzz/status/1175305089541529600</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不只是聲量很吵，各方面都跟日本人不一樣啊，服裝、眼鏡的品味、髮型、行為舉止、散發的氣氛全部不一樣，只要是日本人都能夠分出來吧」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKg.jpg&h=c21a4ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lordkoropokuru/status/1175318314077192192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flordkoropokuru%2Fstatus%2F1175318314077192192&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=59e9d05b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flordkoropokuru%2Fstatus%2F1175318314077192192&h=ff1f30de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lordkoropokuru/status/1175318314077192192</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「音量很大聲，愛穿顯眼的原色巴塔哥尼亞、北臉之類的品牌運動服，服裝雖然很土但配件卻都要名牌，音量很大聲（說兩次）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKk.jpg&h=95b55bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hourouw/status/1175305880876867584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhourouw%2Fstatus%2F1175305880876867584&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=b8401919\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhourouw%2Fstatus%2F1175305880876867584&h=b7e98ed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hourouw/status/1175305880876867584</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「黑髮、黑框眼鏡、穿搭以原色為主、臉大氣色好、聲音有夠大」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlqedrKo.jpg&h=11ff550e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CA1PA/status/1175883140226699264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCA1PA%2Fstatus%2F1175883140226699264&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=d9b59808\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCA1PA%2Fstatus%2F1175883140226699264&h=79c35ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CA1PA/status/1175883140226699264</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「阿拉蕾（丁小雨（小雲））的眼鏡、上下不搭的服裝（上粉紅下水藍之類的）、男生頭髮兩邊都愛推，一看就知道了」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/27/98/qJeXpqOZlqedrKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F27%2F98%2FqJeXpqOZlq